adviseScripts.text: Pit Boss...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: How do you think Blanc manages to be so charming all the time?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Because of her lively personality.
Personally, I think you're much more adorable.
Wow!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: You knew immediately what your answer was going to be.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: That's amazing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Um...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I appreciate you saying that,
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: but it's Blanc that I want to discuss, not me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I know you were saying that just to make me feel better...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Noir and I chat about Blanc's allure for a while.
Pit Boss,
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: people always look at me when I pass by them.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: It's really embarrassing... why do you think they do that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Because your outfit stands out a fair bit.
Because you're so pretty.
I knew it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I wear this same outfit every day, but I still haven't gotten used to it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Th-that can't be it!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Oh jeez, now I'm even more embarrassed...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I have a brief chat with Noir.
Pit Boss,
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: will you be coming to the show tonight?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Yes, I will.
Sorry, I don't have time.
Oh man...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I've been slacking off with my practice lately.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: If you come, I'm afraid I'll get all nervous and end up making mistakes.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: But I'll try my best!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Whoo!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: That's a relief.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I haven't been practicing much recently.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: If you came, I'd be a nervous wreck and mess up my performance. You not coming is a blessing in disguise.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I'll make sure to be prepared for you next time!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I chat a little more with Noir about tonight's show.
I always get so nervous before I go on stage. It's debilitating.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: How can I get over it?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Think of me.
Think about Blanc.
Uh...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I don't think I can.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: That'll only make me more nervous...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: *Sign*
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: B-Blanc...?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Hey, that does seem to calm me down a bit!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Thanks, Pit Boss!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I chat with Noir about how to deal with stage fright.
Pit Boss!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Have you ever heard of the carrot song?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: C'mon bunny, hop to it! Catch the carrot!
What is that?
So you know the lyrics, too?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: That's awesome.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I didn't know them until Blanc told me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I guess I'm slow catching up with the newest trends...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: No way!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: You don't know?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Actually, I didn't know about it either, not until Blanc told me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: C'mon bunny, hop to it! Catch the carrot!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: That's how it starts.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Noir and I recite more of the lyrics to the carrot song.
What do you think is the most alluring part of pole dancing?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I've been having a hard time with it recently.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: It's both elegant and sexy.
The exquisite postures and technique.
E-elegant and sexy?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Those words don't seem to quite suit me...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: How exactly do I bring out that side of myself?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Hey, you're right!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Pole dancing is all about pulling off one eye-catching pose after the other.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: And the technique required to string them all together is crucial.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Thanks for helping me see the light, Pit Boss!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I chat with Noir about pole dancing for a while.
People call me and Blanc the lucky bunny twins.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: But what if something unfortunate happens to me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Then you'll be downgraded to a semi-lucky bunny.
Then your luck will have run out.
Will I?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I appreciate your candor...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Then again, I guess a semi-lucky bunny still counts as lucky.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Works for me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: You mean I'd be all out of luck?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Where would I have to go to fill it back up again?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: What if I run out of it on an important day?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Noir and I chat about luck for a while.
Have you ever seen a real bunny?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I've seen the photos. They're so adorable!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Yes, I have.
No, I haven't.
No kidding!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Do they look like they do in the photos?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Are they really like teeny-tiny cotton balls with ears?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Yeah, I guess it's uncommon to come across real animals.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I'm curious if their ears really stick out like in the photos.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: If only I could see one with my own eyes.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I chat with Noir about bunnies for a while.
Rouge was in a foul mood today 'cause her coin landed tails side up.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: To her, it's a bad omen meaning she'll have rotten luck for the rest of the day.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Are there any things that you consider to be bad luck?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I don't think so.
I'm only unlucky that I don't get to see you every day.
That's nice.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Then you must be a pretty lucky guy!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: If you did have something, you'd end up obsessing over it every day like Rouge does.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Don't be silly!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Do you really mean that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Noir and I talk more about bad omens.
Pit Boss, I'm sorry...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I've got pole dancing practice today, so I've got to leave early.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: No problem, we can reschedule for another time.
Sorry, but you can't leave until we finish our session.
Oh!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Thanks for being so understanding.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Our next counseling session can go on for a little longer!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: But...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Blanc will have to wait for me...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Can't you make an exception, just this once?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I let the anxious-looking Noir leave early.
Dogs go "woof".
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Cats go "meow".
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: And rabbits go...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: ... "Bunny, bunny"?
... "Goo goo gah gah"?
I'm not so sure about that...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Bingo!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: That's what I think they sound like too.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Although I'm not 100% sure, to be honest...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I chat with Noir about what sounds bunnies make.
What's the easiest way to make friends?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I'm always cripplingly shy whenever I meet people for the first time.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Start with some small talk.
Find a topic that you're both interested in.
Small talk?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: How do I do that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: It's hard to strike up a conversation without a topic...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Hey, that's a great idea!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: So, you and I could talk about Blanc, for example?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: We'll be fast friends in that case!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I chat with Noir about how to make friends.
I think my hair is too long. Sometimes it gets in the way when I'm pole dancing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Do you think I should get it trimmed?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: It's beautiful as is.
How about tying it up?
You think so?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: ... Thanks.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I guess I'll bear with it then, even if it may hinder my performance.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Ooh!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: That's a great idea!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I'll tie it up next time I perform.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Thank you, Pit Boss.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I chat with Noir about hairstyles that are best suited for the stage.
Um...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Wait until Noir finishes talking.
Ask Noir what's the matter.
D-do...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: ... Do you want to go for a walk in the park with me?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Phew... I finally said it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: You okay?
N-no!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Nothing's wrong... erm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I spend a short counseling session with Noir.
Pit Boss,
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: did you come to Coin Rush yesterday?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Yes, I did.
No, I was in the Commander's Room.
So it was you that I saw!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I couldn't make you out clearly from where I was on the stage,
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: but I was sure that I'd seen someone who looked just like you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Oh, okay...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I thought I saw you in the audience when I was on stage yesterday.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: The audience usually isn't well-lit, so I guess my eyes were playing tricks on me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I have a good counseling session with Noir.
I feel like today is an especially auspicious day.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Can I share my luck with you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Hold out my hand.
Lean my face in closer.
I'll just give a little handshake, and...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Lucky recharge!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Are you feeling lucky?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Uh...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Why are you leaning in so close?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Y-you're making me uncomfortable!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Once our counseling wraps up, Noir fills up my luck.
Pit Boss,
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: do you prefer curvier girls, or slimmer girls?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I prefer curvier girls.
I like both.
I... I see!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Um...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: So you don't like slim girls at all?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Oh!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: You like them both?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: ... That's great!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I had a good time with Noir.
The more I look at Blanc, the more adorable I find her.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I want to be just like her...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: What should I do?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Try on a white bunny costume.
You're twins. You two are very similar.
Hm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Do you think I'll look like Blanc if I dress like that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: What if people make jokes about me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: R-really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: You're right. I can't become her just because I want to.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I am already happy that we're twins.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Noir and I chat about Blanc for a while.
Besides the bunny costume I usually wear,
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: can you recommend any other outfits?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Something less formal.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: A hoodie and jeans.
A swimsuit.
I don't know...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Blanc said that hoodies aren't a good fit for me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: She said it'd make my chest look, to quote her, "obscenely ginormous".
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Anything else?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: A swimsuit?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Um...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I don't think that'd be appropriate for pole dancing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I guess it is a bit more casual than a bunny costume though.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I chat with Noir about clothes for a while.
Pit Boss!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Blanc and I just finished up today's lucky draw.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Would you like to try?
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Draw once.
Draw twice.
Wow!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Today will be a super lucky day for you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Congratulations!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Uh oh...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Unfortunately, today is an unlucky day for you...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: B-but don't worry!
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: I-I'm right here...
adviseScripts.speaker: Noir

adviseScripts.text: Noir and I talk more about today's fortune.
